                <Header>Armel-Leftwich Visitor Center</Header>
                <Paragraph>From March to December, the visitor center is open daily, 9 a.m.–5 p.m. During January and February, the visitor center is open on weekdays, 9 a.m.–4 p.m. The gift shop, however, is open on the weekends, 9 a.m.–5 p.m.</Paragraph>
